description:
Analyze the 'http.cap' capture file at /home/ga/Documents/captures/http.cap to measure specific latency events. Distinguish between Network Latency (TCP Handshake Latency between the initial SYN and SYN-ACK packets) and Application Processing Latency (HTTP Server Processing Latency between the HTTP GET request and the first HTTP 200 OK response). Save a screenshot of the packet list showing the server processing latency measurement to /home/ga/Documents/captures/latency_evidence.png. Create a JSON report at /home/ga/Documents/captures/latency_report.json containing the measurements in seconds using the following format:

{
  "network_latency_seconds": <float>,
  "server_processing_seconds": <float>
}
